{
	"_readme": "Conservative corrected-PPO improvement arm warm-started from the v13-2 incumbent. Relative to fair-v15-incumbent-pfsp, this changes only update aggressiveness: 10x lower learning rate, two epochs, clip 0.10, entropy 0.002, cosine decay, target KL 0.01, and a 0.05 KL-to-pre-update anchor. It retains the PFSP-heavy field, fixed deployment temperature, and aux-off objective. The purpose is to preserve incumbent behavior while accumulating small field-specific improvements instead of the observed late-training regression.",
